				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">If you grab a golem style pet, or sometimes the right undead.... you belnd in with cabbies and necros.
<br />

<br />
Also...
<br />

<br />
the HERE command i did not fully understand at first. it is AMAZING! We have used Stay in the past, but if you tell a pet to stay it will not even more to attack if it is hit. With HERE it does. You can run by a spot and click here when you get over where you want the pet without even breaking stride. He goes there, but then for all intents and purposes acts as if he were on follow, and you were standing right next to him.
<br />

<br />
Needs a bit more testing, but it gives you a nice new level of control in soem situations.
<br />

<br />
ALSO..... Shard Golems are sweet pets. Big white bastards are huge. Bu no matter how big he was, when i went into, or came out of, the keep he followed me without fail. <img src="images/smiles/icon_smile.gif" alt="icon_smile.gif" border="0" /></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
